Arithmetic_key3: Arithmetic `operators` ka use numeric value  ke sath common mathematical  operation karne ke liye use karte hai.
Arithmetic_key28: **Addition :-**  Additional operate kissi bhi value ko add krne ke liye use hota hai.
Arithmetic_key32: **Subtraction :-** Subtraction `operator` ek value ko dusri value se gatane  ke liye use krte hai.
Arithmetic_key36: **Multiply :-** Multiply operate kiss bhi value ko guna krne ke kaam aata hai.
Arithmetic_key40: **Division :-** Divsion `operator` kissi bhi ek value ko dursi value se divide krne ke kaam aata hai.
Arithmetic_key44: **Modulus :-** Modulus operate kissi bhi ek value ko durse se divide krne ke baad jo reminder aata hai woh result mai deta hai.
Arithmetic_key48: **Exponents :-** Exponents operate kissi bhi ek value ko dusri value ko multiple krta hai.
